Visual Technology Inc said a groupled by &lt;Hambrecht and Quist Group> has acquired majorityownership of Visual for 9,250,000 dlrs in equity financing.    The company said Hambrecht and Quist president William R.Hambrecht and three other Hambrecht and Quist representativeshave been named to the Visual board, with Robert M. Morrill,managing partner of the Boston office of Hambrecht's Hambrechtand Quist Venture Partners unit named chairman.  Clifford G.Zimmer Jr. remains president and chief executive officer.    Visual also said about nine mln dlrs of its debt has beenconverted to equity. Reuter&#3;